sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagram 54: Live Commerce Realtime Interaction Flow

  autonumber
  actor V as Vendor
  actor B as Buyer
  participant API as Live API
  participant LK as Live Streaming Layer
  participant Meta as Session Metadata Store
  participant Chat as Realtime Chat
  participant Order as Cart and Order Service

  V->>API: Start live session
  API->>LK: Create stream room and access policy
  API->>Meta: Save session status=live viewer_count=0
  LK-->>V: Publish stream

  B->>API: Join live session
  API->>LK: Issue viewer token
  API->>Meta: Increment viewer_count and presence
  LK-->>B: Stream subscribed

  B->>Chat: Send message and reaction
  Chat-->>V: Realtime interaction updates

  V->>LK: Pin product overlay
  LK-->>B: Shoppable overlay update

  B->>Order: Add to cart or quick checkout from overlay
  Order-->>B: Cart or order updated
  Order->>Meta: Update conversion metrics for session

  alt Stream disruption
    B->>LK: Reconnect with backoff
    LK-->>B: Resume session continuity
    API->>Meta: Restore viewer presence
  end
